00:18.117 --> 00:19.874
I woke up I didn't know

00:19.942 --> 00:21.120
where I was.

00:21.188 --> 00:24.332
Didn't know who I was.

00:24.400 --> 00:26.520
Couldn't believe I'd slept

00:26.588 --> 00:29.173
through most of my life.

00:29.241 --> 00:31.694
I'd been unconscious for 22

00:31.762 --> 00:36.324
years. Since 1989. I was 18.

00:36.398 --> 00:38.305
And the accident happened

00:38.373 --> 00:39.718
at a construction site,

00:39.786 --> 00:40.924
is that right?

00:40.992 --> 00:42.436
Yes, it was a summer job.

00:42.504 --> 00:43.609
I was installing a church

00:43.677 --> 00:46.726
steeple. A crane collapsed.

00:46.794 --> 00:47.965
I don't even remember it hitting

00:48.033 --> 00:49.809
me. One second, it was

00:49.877 --> 00:51.381
a beautiful day, the next,

00:51.449 --> 00:53.356
phhtt... lights out.

00:53.424 --> 00:55.399
And what exactly is it that

00:55.466 --> 00:56.741
brought you here? What don't you

00:56.809 --> 00:58.916
like about yourself?

00:58.984 --> 01:00.524
Jesus, man, look at me.

01:00.591 --> 01:02.096
I'm ancient!

01:02.164 --> 01:05.410
Even though my body was alive

01:05.477 --> 01:07.586
for 40 years, I was only awake

01:07.654 --> 01:08.824
for 18.

01:08.892 --> 01:10.732
And you want to look like

01:10.800 --> 01:12.303
an 18 year old again?

01:12.371 --> 01:14.411
I am an 18 year old!

01:14.479 --> 01:17.658
I had plans before I went in

01:17.726 --> 01:18.696
the coma. I was gonna go to

01:18.763 --> 01:20.100
college. I was gonna meet

01:20.167 --> 01:22.007
a girl, have a family.

01:22.075 --> 01:24.548
Have a career.

01:24.618 --> 01:25.552
Mr. Kenny...

01:25.622 --> 01:26.658
See, that's...

01:26.725 --> 01:29.902
I'm a mister. I'm a mister now.

01:32.009 --> 01:35.085
I look in the mirror and I see

01:35.152 --> 01:37.258
this old man looking back at me.

01:37.325 --> 01:40.334
And I'm like, "who are you?

01:40.402 --> 01:44.480
Who put me in your body?"

01:44.547 --> 01:46.788
I need you to make the outside

01:46.856 --> 01:50.430
match the inside. You can give

01:50.497 --> 01:52.368
me a chance to live all those

01:52.436 --> 01:53.673
years that I lost for the first

01:53.741 --> 01:56.146
time, fully awake.

01:56.214 --> 01:59.287
You can give me back my life.

