04:00.088 --> 04:01.321
Oh. Ok.

04:01.389 --> 04:03.556
Well, you haven't exactly

04:03.624 --> 04:04.590
thanked me for what I've done

04:04.658 --> 04:05.925
here.

04:05.992 --> 04:06.792
Can't imagine how that

04:06.860 --> 04:08.126
slipped my mind.

04:08.194 --> 04:10.895
Look, I know it takes

04:10.963 --> 04:12.229
a little bit of getting used to,

04:12.297 --> 04:13.864
but in the overcrowded markets

04:13.931 --> 04:15.232
in L.A., you need to make

04:15.299 --> 04:17.502
bold style choices.

04:17.570 --> 04:19.774
And speaking of style, could you

04:19.841 --> 04:20.875
please get up off the couch

04:20.942 --> 04:22.949
