04:24.789 --> 04:25.655
This is the third time

04:25.723 --> 04:26.689
you tried to drag me out this

04:26.757 --> 04:27.523
week, all right? I didn't get

04:27.591 --> 04:28.857
married so that you could get me

04:28.925 --> 04:30.292
in a suit and have me rub elbows

04:30.359 --> 04:34.628
with the great unwashed.

04:36.796 --> 04:39.030
All right.

04:39.098 --> 04:41.265
Look, I got the house, the job,

04:41.333 --> 04:43.533
the beautiful wife. Just let me

04:43.600 --> 04:45.267
relax and enjoy my life.

04:48.337 --> 04:50.638
Ok.

04:55.643 --> 04:56.980
Awesome ballgame last night.

04:57.048 --> 04:59.083
You get to catch it?

04:59.151 --> 05:00.284
Is that you?

05:00.352 --> 05:01.051
Huh?

05:01.119 --> 05:02.419
You stink.

05:02.487 --> 05:04.088
And you look like shit.

05:04.156 --> 05:05.289
Thank you.

05:05.357 --> 05:06.090
