05:27.419 --> 05:29.320
Trying to find a bed.

05:29.388 --> 05:30.221
Only have a mattress on

05:30.289 --> 05:31.089
the floor right now.

05:31.157 --> 05:32.190
A man over thirty should

05:32.258 --> 05:33.391
never buy anything that he has

05:33.459 --> 05:34.357
to put together, particularly

05:34.425 --> 05:35.756
from the swedes.

05:35.823 --> 05:36.989
Mm-hmm.

