05:48.730 --> 05:49.764
Kimber?

05:49.832 --> 05:53.767
Matter of fact...

05:53.835 --> 05:55.969
You'd be doing me a huge favor.

05:56.037 --> 05:57.270
She's being a real pain in

05:57.338 --> 05:59.739
