06:20.892 --> 06:22.526
Hi.

06:22.594 --> 06:23.830
Hi.

06:23.898 --> 06:25.232
Sorry to keep you waiting,

06:25.299 --> 06:26.366
Mrs., um...

06:26.433 --> 06:27.200
Banks.

06:27.267 --> 06:27.867
Banks.

06:27.935 --> 06:28.568
Willow Banks.

06:28.635 --> 06:29.902
Willow Banks. Wow.

06:29.970 --> 06:31.637
Beautiful. Dr. Christian Troy.

06:32.639 --> 06:33.939
You a model?

06:34.006 --> 06:35.106
I was.

06:35.174 --> 06:35.974
Great.

06:36.042 --> 06:37.342
I'd like to apologize

06:37.409 --> 06:38.376
for the receptionist. She can

06:38.443 --> 06:39.443
be a real bitch sometimes.

06:39.511 --> 06:40.477
Dr. Troy...

06:40.545 --> 06:41.578
