06:55.691 --> 06:57.692
Ahh.

07:02.231 --> 07:03.598
Maybe I should bang

07:03.666 --> 07:05.700
the shit out of you right here

07:05.768 --> 07:09.671
on this desk.

07:09.739 --> 07:13.675
Dr. Troy?

07:13.743 --> 07:16.144
Dr. Troy? Excuse me?

07:16.212 --> 07:18.646
Yes. So...

07:18.714 --> 07:21.115
What can I do for you,

07:21.183 --> 07:24.185
Ms. Banks? I'd ask you what you

07:24.252 --> 07:25.152
don't like about yourself,

07:25.220 --> 07:26.420
but you look pretty good to me.

07:27.655 --> 07:28.822
Well, that's exactly

07:28.890 --> 07:29.957
the problem.

07:30.024 --> 07:30.924
Right.

07:30.992 --> 07:31.792
I'm tired of all

07:31.859 --> 07:32.492
the attention I get because

07:32.560 --> 07:34.294
of the way I look. I'm tired

07:34.362 --> 07:35.996
of every guy I meet either being

07:36.063 --> 07:37.230
too intimidated to talk to me,

07:37.298 --> 07:38.965
or think that he can just stroll

07:39.033 --> 07:40.166
up and ask me out.

07:40.234 --> 07:41.334
Hmm.

07:41.402 --> 07:42.101
I can't tell you how many

07:42.169 --> 07:43.002
times a guy has tried some

07:43.069 --> 07:43.969
cheesy pick-up line or howled

07:44.037 --> 07:46.271
like a dog as I walk by. I mean,

07:46.339 --> 07:48.173
is it too much to ask for just

07:48.241 --> 07:49.308
a little conversation before

07:49.375 --> 07:50.308
telling me that you're

07:50.376 --> 07:51.843
envisioning me naked?

07:52.979 --> 07:53.779
And I'm tired of not having

07:53.846 --> 07:54.813
any girlfriends because they

07:54.881 --> 07:57.149
think I make them look bad.

07:57.216 --> 07:59.951
I just...I can't be perfect

08:00.019 --> 08:01.686
anymore.

08:01.754 --> 08:04.022
I want to be unperfect.

08:04.089 --> 08:05.490
Unperfect?

08:05.557 --> 08:07.992
Mm-hmm. Yeah.

08:09.894 --> 08:11.395
Well, that's the stupidest thing

08:11.462 --> 08:12.429
I ever heard.

08:13.364 --> 08:15.131
People come in here every day

08:15.199 --> 08:15.832
asking for what you have.

08:15.900 --> 08:17.133
They want your face.

08:17.201 --> 08:18.835
Well, I don't. Not any

08:18.903 --> 08:20.670
longer. It's just too much

08:20.738 --> 08:23.473
pressure, Dr. Troy. I feel like

08:23.541 --> 08:25.441
I'm onstage all the time.

08:25.509 --> 08:27.277
I even quit modeling, and that

08:27.344 --> 08:29.479
hasn't helped. Look, for once in

08:29.547 --> 08:30.980
my life, I just want to be able

08:31.048 --> 08:32.982
to walk down the street

08:33.049 --> 08:34.817
and be ignored.

08:34.885 --> 08:35.985
I want to be normal looking.

08:36.052 --> 08:37.720
I want to be average.

08:37.787 --> 08:38.386
What about putting on

08:38.455 --> 08:39.087
a couple of pounds? You know,

08:39.155 --> 08:40.255
a double cheeseburger,

08:40.323 --> 08:41.056
something like that.

08:41.124 --> 08:41.990
I don't eat red meat.

08:42.058 --> 08:43.024
Ice cream.

08:43.092 --> 08:44.092
I'm lactose intolerant.

08:44.159 --> 08:45.927
Jesus.

08:45.995 --> 08:47.128
You know what I'm talking about.

08:47.196 --> 08:48.963
Just take worse care of

08:49.031 --> 08:50.898
yourself. Like some nuts?

08:50.966 --> 08:51.799
No, thanks.

08:51.867 --> 08:53.067
Come on, you might enjoy it.

08:53.135 --> 08:54.235
Look, I said I wanted to be

08:54.303 --> 08:55.936
unbeautiful, not unhealthy.

08:56.004 --> 08:57.337
Ok.

08:57.405 --> 08:58.305
And I have tried to make

08:58.372 --> 08:59.838
superficial changes. I'm not

08:59.906 --> 09:01.105
wearing any make-up, I haven't

09:01.173 --> 09:02.805
washed my hair in like a week.

09:02.872 --> 09:03.738
I mean, look at what I'm

09:03.806 --> 09:04.972
wearing, for Christ sakes.

09:05.040 --> 09:07.273
And still, your parking valet

09:07.341 --> 09:07.939
gave me his phone number.

09:08.007 --> 09:10.473
Well, you'll just have to try

09:10.540 --> 09:11.871
a little harder, because looking

09:11.939 --> 09:13.271
the way you look, I would never

09:13.339 --> 09:14.371
touch you with a scalpel.

09:14.438 --> 09:16.203
And good luck finding a doctor

09:16.270 --> 09:19.502
who would.

09:29.770 --> 09:33.474
Phew.

09:33.542 --> 09:34.844
Hey.

09:34.912 --> 09:35.612
Hey.

09:35.680 --> 09:37.047
Oh, hello. Heh. Do you want

09:37.115 --> 09:37.949
