10:46.807 --> 10:48.674
Hmm.

10:48.742 --> 10:50.075
Hmm?

10:50.143 --> 10:52.944
Or you could do kind of a homey,

10:53.012 --> 10:54.912
kick-back, country French look?

10:54.980 --> 10:56.813
Look, do I need to go to

10:56.881 --> 10:58.081
therapy just to get some

10:58.149 --> 10:59.249
