10:59.316 --> 11:00.583
That's why I hired you.

11:00.651 --> 11:03.251
No, it's just, in design

11:03.319 --> 11:05.319
school, they really emphasize on

11:05.387 --> 11:06.753
listening to the client.

11:06.821 --> 11:08.121
You know, like your likes,

11:08.188 --> 11:09.155
dislikes, colors.

11:09.222 --> 11:10.422
Yeah, well, this particular

11:10.490 --> 11:13.557
client has no self, it seems.

11:13.625 --> 11:15.158
He's arrived in his 45th year

11:15.226 --> 11:16.360
with no opinions or taste of his

11:16.427 --> 11:18.761
own. He spent too much time in

11:18.829 --> 11:20.195
everyone else's shadow.

11:20.263 --> 11:22.831
Kimber, just do your thing.

11:22.898 --> 11:24.298
You know, whatever you think.

11:24.366 --> 11:26.600
Let your imagination go,

11:26.667 --> 11:27.767
you have my permission.

11:27.835 --> 11:28.735
Yeah?

11:28.802 --> 11:30.903
Yeah.

11:30.970 --> 11:33.705
Ok. Well, I think I can do

11:33.772 --> 11:37.174
something in here.

11:37.241 --> 11:39.375
Thank you.

11:39.443 --> 11:41.244
I promise you, I'm going to blow

11:41.311 --> 11:43.346
you away with this place, ok?

11:43.414 --> 11:45.247
I have total faith in you.

11:45.315 --> 11:47.148
Thanks.

11:47.216 --> 11:48.116
I'll see you later.

11:48.183 --> 11:49.050
Ok.

11:49.117 --> 11:49.717
